@startuml Kinesis Sensor Pipeline
!theme sketchy-outline
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Factory\nSensors" as sensor
participant "RPi\nGateway" as rpi
database "SQLite\nBuffer" as sqlite
participant "Kinesis\nData Streams" as kinesis
participant "Kinesis\nFirehose" as firehose
participant "S3\nData Lake" as s3
participant "Lambda\nProcessing" as lambda
participant "Step\nFunctions" as stepfn
database "Time-Series\nDB" as tsdb
participant "CloudWatch\n+ Sentry" as cw
actor "BI Tools\n(Grafana/PowerBI)" as bi

== Data Ingestion ==

sensor -> rpi: Readings\nevery 5 min

rpi -> kinesis: Send data\n(when online)
kinesis -> firehose: Stream data
firehose -> s3: Batch write

== Offline Resilience ==

rpi <-> sqlite: Buffer data\n(when offline)
sqlite -> kinesis: Sync buffered\ndata on reconnection

== Processing & Analytics ==

s3 -> lambda: Trigger processing
lambda -> lambda: Parse, compute\ncosts, validate
lambda -> tsdb: Store processed data
lambda --> cw: Logs & metrics

stepfn -> s3: Orchestrate ETL\n(external data)
stepfn -> tsdb: Load transformed data

tsdb --> bi: Query analytics

@enduml